Text.Page: Move along, pal. You got the wrong enchanter.
Someday, friend, we'll learn to choose wiser leaders. Today's not the day.

At the request of the exarch, I currently offer silver quality enchanting. My silver enchanting is more successful than my bronze, friend. If you want an even higher standard, ask your exarch to change it to gold.
